description:
This is a 24 minute workout called '20 Minute 2nd Trimester Prenatal Cardio Workout-- (but good for ALL Trimesters of Pregnancy!)' from the channel BodyFit By Amy.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Get your heart pumping in a gentle yet effective way to stay fit during pregnancy and prepare for delivery and recovery.  Made for 2nd trimester, but safe and appropriate for any trimester of pregnancy,
